# QTIP + Insights Platform — Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
This is a unified QA + Training + Reporting platform 
built with React 19 + TypeScript frontend and 
Express + Prisma + MySQL backend.

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React 19 with TypeScript
- Vite
- React Router v7
- TanStack Query v5 for all server state
- TanStack Table v8 for all data grids
- Tailwind CSS 3 for styling
- shadcn/ui for ALL UI components 
  (buttons, inputs, dialogs, dropdowns, tables, forms)
- Tremor for dashboard components 
  (KPI cards, metric tiles, charts, progress bars)
- Recharts for all chart rendering (via Tremor)
- react-querybuilder for filter/query builder UI
- React Hook Form for all forms
- dnd-kit for drag and drop
- TipTap for rich text / course slide editor
- lucide-react for all icons
- Axios for API calls

### Backend
- Node.js with TypeScript
- Express 5
- Prisma ORM for ALL database operations
- MySQL 8
- JWT authentication (access + refresh tokens)
- Zod for validation
- Winston for logging
- Multer for file uploads
- xlsx for Excel import/export

## Design Rules
- ALWAYS use shadcn/ui components first. 
  Never create raw HTML buttons, inputs, or 
  form elements.
- ALWAYS use Tremor for any dashboard metric 
  cards, KPI tiles, or chart wrappers.
- ALWAYS use TanStack Table for any data table 
  or grid — never build custom table HTML.
- ALWAYS use TanStack Query for API calls — 
  never use useEffect + fetch or axios directly 
  in components.
- ALWAYS use React Hook Form for any form with 
  more than 2 fields.
- ALWAYS use lucide-react for icons — never use 
  emoji or other icon libraries.
- Use Tailwind utility classes for layout and 
  spacing. Do not write custom CSS files.
- All colors should use Tailwind slate/blue palette 
  to stay consistent with shadcn/ui defaults.

## Navigation Structure
The app has three top-level sections:
1. Quality — QA forms, submissions, disputes, 
   scoring, QA analytics
2. Training — courses, training paths, coaching 
   sessions, enrollments, certificates, quizzes
3. Insights — dashboards, report builder, data 
   explorer, raw data export, import center

## Role System
Roles in order of access level:
- admin (full access)
- director (org-wide reporting, no system config)
- manager (team/department level)
- qa (quality management)
- trainer (training content and coaching)
- csr (own data only)

## API Base URL
All API calls use: /api/ prefix
Auth token stored in httpOnly cookie.
Use TanStack Query for all data fetching.

## File Structure
- frontend/src/components/ui/ — shadcn components 
  (auto-generated, do not edit)
- frontend/src/components/common/ — shared reusable 
  components built by us
- frontend/src/components/quality/ — Quality section
- frontend/src/components/training/ — Training section  
- frontend/src/components/insights/ — Insights section
- frontend/src/components/admin/ — Admin screens
- frontend/src/hooks/ — custom React hooks
- frontend/src/services/ — Axios API service functions
- frontend/src/types/ — TypeScript interfaces
